rest.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20daughter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68137461a466d2b74ab4b2f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20as%20a%20solo%20parent%2C%20Mother's%20Day%20doesn't%20look%20traditional%20for%20her.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20single%20mom%20to%20a%20toddler%2C%20and%20Mother's%20Day%20doesn't%20include%20fancy%20brunches%20and%20flowers%20for%20me.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20year%2C%20I'm%20dropping%20off%20my%203-year-old%20for%20one%20day%20with%20my%20mom%20so%20I%20can%20rest.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20extraordinary%20job%20I'm%20doing%20as%20a%20mother.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20single%20mom%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-deserves-time-alone-mothers-day-gift-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMother's%20Day%20has%20never%20looked%20quite%20as%20curated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20picture-perfect%20brunches%20and%20bouquets%20I%20see%20splashed%20across%20social%20media.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-uk-mothers-day-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eleisurely%20breakfast%20in%20bed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I'm%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20woken%20at%206%20a.m.%20by%20the%20calls%20for%20%26quot%3BMama!%26quot%3B%20from%20my%20adorably%20persistent%20alarm%20clock.%20Without%20a%20partner%20to%20make%20plans%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20find%20a%20new%20path%20to%20celebrate%20Mother's%20Day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e4a6014-066e-42b1-a5ec-8ab11387eaf8%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20Mother's%20Day%20was%20a%20blur%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-daughter-wont-call-me-on-mothers-day-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20first%20Mother's%20Day%20was%20a%20blur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20newborn%20snuggles%20and%20sleep%20deprivation.%20My%20daughter%2C%20Via%2C%20was%20one%20week%20old%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20my%20tiny%2C%20wrinkled%20baby%20that%20every%20moment%20with%20her%20felt%20like%20a%20celebration.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20no%20plans%20beyond%20washing%20bottles%20and%20feeling%20her%20fist%20grip%20around%20my%20finger.%20Last%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-lives-san-diego-spends-three-months-bali-yearly-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewe%20were%20living%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Mother's%20Day%20wasn't%20on%20the%20local%20calendar%20(they%20celebrate%20in%20December%2C%20instead)%2C%20so%20it%20again%20passed%20without%20plans%20or%20special%20recognition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20however%2C%20feels%20different.%20Via%20is%203%20years%20old%3B%20she's%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20curiosity%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20increasing%20independence.%20I'd%20love%20to%20do%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonor-mom-anniversary-death-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esomething%20meaningful%20on%20Mother's%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Yet%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20traditional%20celebration%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20often%20involves%20a%20partner's%20thoughtful%20planning%20and%20execution%20%E2%80%94%20feels%20like%20adding%20another%20task%20onto%20my%20already%20overflowing%20plate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20working%20single%20mom%2C%20the%20mental%20and%20emotional%20labor%20of%20planning%2C%20deciding%2C%20preparing%2C%20arranging%2C%20and%20managing%20is%20never-ending.%20Adding%20the%20pressure%20of%20creating%20a%20Pinterest-worthy%20Mother's%20Day%20feels%20less%20like%20a%20celebration%20and%20more%20like%20another%20%26quot%3Bto-do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8bf5b62-f010-4ae5-a085-f32ef3e0249b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20dropping%20my%20toddler%20off%20with%20my%20mom%20for%20a%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20considered%20not%20making%20any%20plans%20and%20letting%20the%20day%20once%20again%20pass%20without%20notice%2C%20but%20I%20also%20feel%20that%20this%20incredible%20journey%20of%20motherhood%20deserves%20special%20recognition.%20I%20decided%20to%20split%20the%20weekend%20into%20two%20parts.%20On%20the%20Friday%20before%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20I'm%20dropping%20Via%20off%20with%20my%20mom%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoddler-sleep-regression-checke-into-a-hotel-to-sleep-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esleep-cation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Every%20time%20I%20catch%20up%20on%20rest%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself%3B%20the%20best%20gift%20I%20could%20give%20myself%20this%20Mother's%20Day%20is%20to%20show%20up%20for%20the%20day%20recharged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20booked%20a%20night%20at%20the%20nearby%20resort%20and%20a%20dinner%20reservation%20at%20an%20upscale%20Chinese%20restaurant%20I've%20wanted%20to%20try.%20I'm%20going%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20next%20day%20and%20stay%20in%20bed%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20morning%20before%20heading%20to%20brunch.%20Then%2C%20on%20the%20way%20home%2C%20I'm%20stopping%20for%20an%20ultra-relaxing%20massage.%20A%20nice%20dinner%2C%20a%20serene%20resort%2C%20sleeping%20in%2C%20and%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20spa%20%E2%80%94%20to%20me%2C%20this%20is%20the%20ult