0the%20strategies%20I'd%20suggest%20you%20try%20in%20your%20effort%20to%20persuade%20your%20wife%20that%20she%20ought%20to%20get%20a%20part-time%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20evidence.%20There%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20ways%20you%20can%20gather%20evidence.%20One%2C%20you%20can%20go%20through%20your%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-banks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecredit%20card%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20statements%20and%20tally%20the%20incomings%20and%20outgoings.%20This%20should%20give%20both%20of%20you%20a%20clear%20idea%20of%20which%20will%20be%20more%20effective%20%E2%80%94%20cutting%20frivolous%20spending%20or%20earning%20more%20to%20cover%20your%20necessary%20expenditures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20you%20can%20quit%20Grubhubbing%20for%20a%20while%20and%20tighten%20your%20belt%20as%20far%20as%20it%20can.%20Let%20your%20wife%20experience%20the%20evidence.%20Pinching%20pennies%20and%20locking%20down%20the%20budget%20is%20always%20easy%20in%20theory.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20we%20overestimate%20the%20impact%20of%20our%20%2415%20Spotify%20memberships%2C%20%2440%20a%20month%20in%20streaming%20TV%2C%20and%20%24150%20a%20month%20spent%20on%20takeout.%20But%20we%20can't%20know%20how%20much%20it's%20affecting%20our%20bottom%20line%20until%20we%20cut%20the%20spending%20and%20find%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThird%2C%20you%20can%20appeal%20to%20reason.%20Reasoning%20with%20your%20wife%20will%20take%20significant%20and%20intentional%20empathy%20on%20your%20part.%20To%20change%20anyone's%20mind%2C%20you%20must%20first%20intimately%20understand%20their%20perspective.%20Figure%20out%20why%20she%20is%20resisting%20getting%20a%20second%20job.%20Maybe%20she%20doesn't%20feel%20up%20to%20adding%20something%20so%20large%20to%20her%20plate%2C%20maybe%20the%20idea%20of%20delivering%20food%20isn't%20appealing%20to%20her%2C%20maybe%20she%20isn't%20as%20concerned%20about%20your%20financial%20position%2C%20or%20maybe%20she%20has%20a%20particular%20expense%20in%20mind%20that%2C%20if%20cut%2C%20will%20save%20the%20day.%20It%20could%20be%20any%20number%20of%20reasons%2C%20but%20getting%20through%20to%20her%20will%20require%20knowing%20which%20one%20it%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20she%20is%20hung%20up%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20second%20job%20seems%20miserable%20or%20too%20time-consuming%2C%20you%20could%20have%20her%20ride%20along%20with%20you.%20You%20mentioned%20feeling%20like%20she%20wants%20you%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20by%20yourself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20imagine%20this%20is%20a%20very%20lonely%20feeling%20for%20you.%20Sometimes%2C%20this%20type%20of%20frustration%20can%20lead%20us%20to%20behave%20competitively%20in%20our%20relationships.%20We%20complain%20and%20moan%20and%20do%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20to%20show%20our%20partners%20we're%20working%20the%20hardest%20and%20are%20therefore%20the%20most%20exhausted.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20show%20even%20a%20glimmer%20of%20joy%20while%20we%20work%20because%20we%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20mistakenly%20believe%20we%20enjoy%20working%20harder%20than%20they%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20unfortunate%20consequence%20of%20this%20attitude%20is%20that%20we're%20not%20making%20our%20efforts%20very%20attractive%2C%20so%20of%20course%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20join%20us%2C%20and%20so%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20alone.%20So%2C%20show%20your%20wife%20it%20can%20be%20fun.%20Talk%20about%20how%20much%20you%20enjoy%20the%20alone%20time%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20your%20podcasts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Grubhub%20may%20simply%20not%20fit%20your%20wife's%20temperament%20or%20lifestyle.%20Just%20because%20it's%20worked%20for%20you%20and%20getting%20her%20set%20up%20would%20be%20a%20cinch%2C%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20her%20best%20or%20only%20option.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20convince%20your%20wife%20to%20get%20a%20part%20time%20job%20is%20to%20suggest%20things%20you%20know%20she%20would%20love.%20Maybe%20she%20could%20pick%20up%20shifts%20as%20a%20receptionist%20at%20a%20veterinary%20clinic%2C%20or%20pot%20plants%20at%20the%20local%20nursery.%20When%20your%20hobby%20intersects%20with%20your%20job%2C%20it%20hardly%20feels%20like%20work%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20said%2C%20compromise%20is%20likely%20going%20to%20be%20your%20best%20bet.%20Ideas%20for%20fair%20compromise%20include%20agreeing%20to%20do%20things%20her%20way%20first%2C%20but%20put%20a%20specific%20timeline%20on%20it.%20Or%2C%20you%20could%20ask%20her%20to%20join%20you%20in%20working%20a%20part%20time%20job%2C%20but%20only%20until%20you've%20paid%20off%20your%20debt%20or%20have%20a%20certain%20amount%20in%20your%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20that%20you're%20a%20team.%20Having%20different%20opinions%20doesn't%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20you've%20come%20a%20long%20way%20together.%20No%20matter%20what%20comes%20next%2C%20you've%20had%20each%20other's%20backs%20for%20years%2C%20and%20you%20always%20will.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%2