20and%20other%20products%20even%20as%20others%20are%20cutting%20back%2C%20with%20airlines%20such%20as%20United%20and%20Delta%20reporting%20strong%20demand%20for%20premium%20bookings%20despite%20a%20broader%20slowdown%20in%20domestic%20travel%20demand.%20Major%20hotel%20brands%20like%20Hilton%20and%20Hyatt%20have%20also%20reported%20resilience%20in%20the%20luxury%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20wealthy%20travelers%20who%20are%20still%20spending%2C%20there%20are%20four%20specific%20kinds%20of%20trips%20that%20are%20trending%2C%20according%20to%20Tom%20Marchant%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20the%20luxury%20travel%20company%20Black%20Tomato.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20price%20of%20a%20trip%20organized%20by%20Black%20Tomato%2C%20which%20plans%20bespoke%20travel%20around%20the%20world%2C%20is%20about%20%2440%2C000%2C%20Marchant%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20trips%20can%20range%20from%20%2410%2C000%20to%20hundreds%20of%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarchant%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company's%20clients%20often%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20pretty%20agnostic%20on%20where%20I%20want%20to%20go%2C%20but%20this%20is%20how%20I'm%20looking%20to%20feel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20focus%20on%20specific%20destinations%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20certain%20emotions%20or%20experiences%20that%20luxury%20travelers%20are%20seeking.%20Earlier%20this%20year%20the%20company%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blacktomato.com%2Fus%2Ffeelings-engine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFeelings%20Engine%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20incorporates%20AI%20to%20help%20users%20plan%20a%20trip%20around%20a%20feeling%2C%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20feel%20relaxed%2C%20challenged%2C%20free%2C%20motivated%2C%20or%20many%20other%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20four%20kinds%20of%20trips%20that%20Marchant%20said%20are%20trending%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279145b46-abc7-4ba7-941c-b111469ed6f5%5C%22%3E1.%20The%20earned%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hiker%20%C3%AEn%20mountains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e800c3fe8d39283658205%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrips%20that%20involve%20things%20like%20a%20challenging%20hike%20are%20trending%20with%20luxury%20travelers.%3Cp%3EChristoph%20Wagner%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20Tomato%20has%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20travelers%20seeking%20out%20challenging%20experiences%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bearned%26quot%3B%20through%20more%20than%20just%20how%20much%20they%20pay%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20desire%20to%20challenge%20yourself%2C%20whether%20it's%20through%20a%20trek%20or%20a%20long%20journey%20or%20going%20to%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20cultural%20stimuli%2C%26quot%3B%20Marchant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20kinds%20of%20trips%20are%20often%20viewed%20by%20travelers%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20realities%20of%20day-to-day%20life%2C%20when%20just%20about%20everything%20is%20available%20at%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20type%20of%20trip%20is%20trending%20for%20solo%20travelers%20as%20well%20as%20couple%20and%20families%20who%20want%20to%20get%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20company%20organizes%20%26quot%3BGet%20Lost%26quot%3B%20trips%20in%20which%20the%20client%20is%20dropped%20off%20in%20a%20remote%20destination%20and%20left%20with%20supplies%20to%20navigate%20themselves%20back%20to%20civilization%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20days.%20Esther%20Spengler%2C%20a%20Black%20Tomato%20client%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20her%20%2413%2C000%20%26quot%3BGet%20Lost%26quot%3B%20experience%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-pay-to-get-lost-wilderness-luxury-travel-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorocco%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20more%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Badventure%26quot%3B%20than%20a%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20earned%20experiences%20the%20company%20plans%20are%20river%20rafting%20in%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%2C%20mountain%20treks%20in%20Japan%2C%20or%20quad%20biking%20across%20the%20salt%20pans%20of%20Botswana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca159f06-7e4e-4004-9ef4-758327cdc810%5C%22%3E2.%20In%20search%20of%20silence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20wealthy%20travelers%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20vacation%20is%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20noise%20of%20everyday%20life%2C%20Marchant%20said.%20While%20these%20travelers%20don't%20necessarily%20want%20to%20be%20off-grid%2C%20they%20want%20to%20be%20somewhere%20with%20minimal%20background%20noise%20or%20noise%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20more%20and%20more%20people%20looking%20for%20places%20where%20there%20is%20genuine%20quiet%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20can%20go%20and%20reflect%20or%20just%20feel%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20growing%20trend%20of%20quiet-place%20conservation%20and%20travelers%20seeking%20out%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20parks%2C%26quot%3B%20places%20that%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20experience%20relative%20silence%2C%20or%20nothing%20but%20noises%20from%20the%20natural%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20non-profit%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quietparks.org%2Fwilderness-quiet-parks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuiet%20Parks%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%20awarded%20Zabalo%20River%20in%20Ecuador%20as%20the%20first%20wilderness%20quiet%20park.%20Glacier%20National%20Park%20in%20Montana%20was%20the%20first%20US%20national%20park%20to%20receive%20the%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarchant%20said%20one%20aspect%20of%20this%20trend%20is%20%26quot%3Breading%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20the%20traveler%20says%20they%20want%20to%20go%20somewhere%20quiet%20primarily%20so%20they%20can%20read%20and%20reflect%20without%20any%20distractions.%20He%20said%20reading%20trips%20are%20especially%20popular%20with%20business%20leaders%20who%20feel%20they%20rarely%20have%20time%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20life%20to%20enjoy%20books%20without%20getting%20pulled%20into%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c93566e8-69eb-48f2-8f20-eb2e0b4d3e69%5C%22%3E3.%20Bare%20witness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20look%20up%20at%20sky%20with%20glasses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e82c23fe8d3928365823e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravel%20to%20view%20solar%20eclipses%20is%20booming%2C%20including%20among%20the%20wealthy.%3Cp%3ERONALDO%20SCHEMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20for%20natural%20phenomena%20is%20another%20trend%20among%20Black%20Tomato%20clients%2C%20with%20the%20company%20increasingly%20planning%20trips%20around%20natural%20events%20that%20could%20be%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20years%20ago%20the%20company%20built%20bespoke%20camps%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Patagonia%20so%20its%20clients%20could%20witness%20the%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20in%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20to%20witness%20natural%20phenomena%20like%20eclipses%2C%20the%20northern%20lights%2C%20or%20animal%20migrations%20could%20be%20especially%20appealing%20to%20the%20wealthy%20because%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20very%20different%20from%20their%20daily%20life%2C%20Marchant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20clients%20live%20in%20LA%2C%20so%20traveling%20somewhere%20with%20a%20gorgeous%20villa%2C%20fancy%20pool%2C%20and%20nice%20weather%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20appealing%20to%20them%20since%20it's%20what%20they%20already%20have%20at%20h