s%20can%20balloon%20into%20big-time%20frustrations%20for%20business%20leaders%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuranton%20said%20that%20if%20CEOs'%20big%20question%20around%20AI%20in%202024%20was%20which%20model%20to%20use%2C%20their%20ask%20in%202025%20is%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20my%20money%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20are%20often%20challenges%20around%20implementing%20broad%20use%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScaling%20this%20thing%20from%20a%20tech%20standpoint%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Duranton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20companies%20salvage%20their%20AI%20efforts%2C%20he%20said%2C%20his%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20rule%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20organizations%20allocate%20about%2010%25%20of%20their%20effort%20and%20money%20to%20the%20algorithms%20%E2%80%94%20to%20build%20AI%20engines%20or%20train%20LLMs.%20Another%2020%25%20should%20be%20reserved%20for%20data%20and%20technology.%20Essentially%2C%20that's%20to%20make%20the%20AI%20work%20in%20a%20company's%20tech%20environment%2C%20Duranton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20of%20the%20effort%20%E2%80%94%20the%20remaining%2070%25%20%E2%80%94%20should%20go%20to%20changing%20the%20way%20people%20work%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssuming%20you%20have%20a%20technology%20that%20can%20scale%2C%20you%20need%20to%20bring%20that%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people.%20It's%20a%20massive%20change%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Duranton%2C%20who's%20based%20in%20the%20company's%20Paris%20office%20and%20oversees%20BCG%20X's%20global%20army%20of%20nearly%203%2C000%20technologists%2C%20scientists%2C%20programmers%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad9e7cfa-bbef-498c-bb92-28f743ba64bf%5C%22%3ESome%20companies%20are%20struggling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies'%20frustration%20is%20real.%20In%20the%20final%20months%20of%202024%2C%20BCG%20surveyed%20some%201%2C800%20C-suite%20execs%20from%20big%20companies%20in%20nearly%2020%20countries%20and%20found%20that%20while%2075%25%20of%20respondents%20ranked%20AI%20among%20their%20top-three%20priorities%2C%20only%2025%25%20reported%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20value%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20more%20value%2C%20Duranton%20recommends%20that%20companies%20not%20try%20to%20do%20everything%20all%20at%20once.%20He%20said%20the%20scope%20of%20change%20that%20companies%20need%20likely%20can't%20be%20achieved%20with%20tens%20or%20hundreds%20of%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20the%20plan.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20a%20very%20few%20things%2C%20and%20the%20things%20that%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuranton%20said%20companies%20sometimes%20also%20look%20to%20%26quot%3Bincremental%20initiatives.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20he%20thinks%20that's%20often%20a%20mistake.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20companies%20should%20home%20in%20on%20a%20few%20%26quot%3Bquintessential%26quot%3B%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20retailer%2C%20Duranton%20said%2C%20this%20might%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20ensure%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20has%20the%20perfect%20product%20mix%20for%20that%20location%20to%20better%20withstand%20competitors%20nearby%20and%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20CEOs%20understand%20the%20stakes%2C%20Duranton%20said.%20They'll%20often%20tell%20him%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20if%20I%20don't%20do%20that%20better%20than%20others%2C%20I'm%20cooked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuranton%20said%20another%20imperative%20for%20a%20retailer%20might%20be%20to%20develop%20an%20AI%20agent%20that%20can%20shop%20for%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that's%20so%20good%20that%20users%20won't%20want%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20those%20two%20things%2C%20you%20have%20both%20a%20strategic%20agenda%20and%20an%20AI%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20making%20sure%20inventory%20is%20dialed%20and%20the%20shopping%20bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trick%2C%20then%2C%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20focus%20on%20those%20efforts%2C%20Duranton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20quintessentials%2C%20that's%20where%20you%20put%20all%20your%20money%2C%20all%20your%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That's%20necessary%2C%20Duranton%20said%2C%20if%20companies%20want%20to%20take%20the%2010%25%2C%2020%25%2C%2070%25%20approach%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269424957-1e99-48f6-bc3d-c7a8a6c668ed%5C%22%3EAI's%20Bermuda%20Triangle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20scaling%20AI%20is%20also%20often%20difficult%20because%20companies%20can%20feel%20pressure%20to%20compromise%20on%20expenses%2C%20quality%20of%20results%2C%20or%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20they're%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20sort%20of%20Bermuda%20Triangle%2C%20where%20it%20is%20either%20costly%20and%20relevant%20with%20a%20good%20latency%2C%20or%20you%20have%20to%20compromise%20on%20one%20of%20the%20three%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20optimize%2C%26quot%3B%20Duranton%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20AI%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it's%20often%20easy%20to%20demonstrate%20some%20tech%20wizardry%20in%20a%20demo.%20What's%20difficult%2C%20Duranton%20said%2C%20is%20handling%20millions%20of%20requests%20every%20day%20and%20producing%20timely%20and%20relevant%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20different%20ballgame%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20to%20succeed%20with%20AI%2C%20Duranton%20said%2C%20companies%20will%20need%20to%20bring%20along%20people%2C%20not%20just%20bots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvest%20in%20change-management%2C%20not%20just%20technology%2C%20and%20have%20your%20fearless%20and%20strongest%20leaders%20be%20in%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-mistake-companies-m