%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20look%20at%20New%20York%2C%20for%20example.%20It%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-congestion-pricing-toll-manhattan-drivers-new-jersey-democrats-commuters-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econgestion%20pricing%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20now.%20If%20you%20switch%20to%20self-driving%20cars%2C%20the%20very%20first%20thing%20you%20do%20away%20with%20is%20traffic%20lights.%20You%20don't%20need%20them%20anymore%20because%20cars%20can%20communicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20capacity%20will%20also%20increase.%20If%20self-driving%20cars%20are%20allowed%20on%20a%20highway%2C%20you%20could%20easily%20reduce%20the%20spacing%20between%20cars%20by%20a%20factor%20of%20two%2C%20which%20would%20double%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnything%20you%20would%20be%20doing%20differently%20if%20you%20were%20behind%20the%20wheel%20at%20Waymo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20biggest%20fan.%20I%20open%20my%20door%20every%20morning%20and%20see%20two%20or%20three%20Waymos%20zipping%20by%20my%20house%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20be%20prouder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20really%20very%2C%20very%20proud.%20The%20leadership%20has%20done%20an%20amazing%20job%20navigating%20and%20has%20really%20earned%20the%20public's%20trust%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20so%20important%20for%20technological%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225329%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d571fa466d2b74ab5781e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Waymo%20drives%20along%20Venice%20Beach%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-cofounder-sebastian-thrun-alphabet-robotaxi-race-competition-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%