E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20novelty%20does%20not%20always%20translate%20to%20repeat%20business.%20The%20duo%20realised%20that%20plantable%20stationery%20was%20treated%20as%20a%20one-time%20gift.%20Even%20though%20it%20was%20impressive%2C%20companies%20were%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20one-time%20buy.%20To%20build%20a%20sustainable%20business%20that%20has%20a%20greater%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20offer%20something%20people%20used%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20moment%20of%20clarity%20arrived%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20While%20offices%20across%20the%20country%20were%20closed%2C%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20were%20busier%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20they%20needed%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20most%20saw%20scrap%2C%20they%20saw%20an%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20when%20we%20got%20the%20idea%20of%20selling%20copier%20paper.%20Paper%20is%20something%20we%20use%20every%20single%20day%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20recycled%20up%20to%20six%20or%20seven%20times%2C%20yet%20most%20of%20it%20still%20ends%20up%20as%20waste.%20So%20we%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20turn%20that%20missed%20opportunity%20into%20something%20meaningful%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ashutosh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20formally%20launched%20Rescript%2C%20starting%20with%20recycled%20copier%20paper.%20It%20may%20not%20have%20had%20the%20glamour%20of%20plantable%20gifts%2C%20but%20it%20had%20consistency%20and%20volume.%20Soon%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348979%2Fcotton-waste-from-factories-sustainable-stationery-rashi-agarwal-roohani-rang-recycled-diary-no