ms%20like%20notebooks%20and%20journals%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlder%20recycled%20paper%20was%20rough%2C%20fibrous%2C%20and%20it%20used%20to%20damage%20printers.%20We%20solved%20that%20by%20designing%20a%20blend%20that%20is%20durable%20and%20safe%20for%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Naren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPaper-making%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20process%20begins%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20waste%20paper%2C%20sourced%20primarily%20from%20packaging%20trimmings%2C%20textbook%20off-cuts%2C%20and%20even%20old%20student%20notebooks.%20This%20material%20is%20sent%20to%20an%20industrial%20mill%20they%20have%20partnered%20with%20under%20a%20contract%20manufacturing%20model.%20They%20do%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20capacity%20for%20full-scale%20industrial%20papermaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20mill%2C%20the%20waste%20is%20segregated%2C%20then%20fed%20into%20a%20pulping%20machine%20that%20adds%20water%20and%20mixes%20the%20material%20into%20a%20fine%20paste.%20This%20pulp%20is%20flattened%20on%20a%20conveyor%2C%20pressed%2C%20and%20dried%20using%20heat%20to%20produce%20massive%20rolls%20of%20recycled%20paper%2C%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20as%20reels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reels%20are%20cut%20into%20A4%2C%20A3%2C%20and%20A5%20sizes%20for%20copier%20paper%20or%20sent%20for%20ruling%20and%20printing%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20notebooks%20and%20journals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20no%20bright%20white%20papers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20bleaching%20agents%20at%20all%2C%20which%20is%20why%20our%20paper%20is%20not%20bright%20white.%20At%20first%2C%20people%20questioned%20it.%20But%20now%2C%20they%20associate%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400838%2Fathangudi-tiles-chettinad-heritage-tamilnadu-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20tone%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20authenticity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashutosh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuality%20control%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20for%20the%20co-founders.%20At%20their%20in-house%20testing%20lab%2C%20each%20batch%20is%20tested%20for%20GSM%2C%20moisture%2C%20fibre%20strength%2C%20and%20uniformity.%20If%20any%20batch%20falls%20short%2C%20it%20is%20sent%20back%20for%20reprocessing.%20Once%20approved%2C%20the%20paper%20is%20shipped%20to%20their%20partnered%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20the%20final%20products%20are%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescript%20does%20not%20use%20any%20bleaching%20agents%20to%20make%20the%20papers%20white%20so%20they%20have%20the%20natural%20tone%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FCopier-Paper-Comparison_11zon-1746711691-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%2